  <brief_title>The INSPIRE Study: Probable Benefit of the Neuro- Spinal Scaffold for Treatment of AIS A Thoracic Acute Spinal Cord Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>The INSPIRE Study: InVivo Study of Probable Benefit of the Neuro-Spinal Scaffold(TM) for Safety and Neurologic Recovery in Subjects With Complete Thoracic AIS A Spinal Cord Injury</official_title>
