  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -  To evaluate whether the Scaffold is safe and demonstrates probable benefit for the
           treatment of complete T2-T12/L1 spinal cord injury .

        -  This is a Humanitarian Device Exemption (HDE) Probable Benefit Study to demonstrate
           safety and probable benefit in support of future studies and an HDE application with
           subsequent approval.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
